        <item>
            <title>冒險樂園掟彩虹模擬器，製作超真實 + 無限掟幣多角度睇有冇「砸界」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/10/jumpin-gym-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jumpin-gym-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/10/jumpin-gym-2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 09:32:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[冒險樂園]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[掟彩虹]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[模擬器]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198316</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>上週六有市民在冒險樂園遊玩掟彩虹時不滿被店員指代幣「砸界」，質疑代幣比彩虹的圖案大兼報警，引起全城熱議。一名網民 BK Hong 昨日在 YouTube 中發布一段短片，遊玩「冒險樂園扔彩虹模擬器」抽水。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1198333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-5.00.34-PM-694x316.png" alt="" width="694" height="316" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-5.00.34-PM-694x316.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-5.00.34-PM-1280x583.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-5.00.34-PM-768x350.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-5.00.34-PM.png 1358w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1198337" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-4.49.33-PM-694x293.png" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-4.49.33-PM-694x293.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-4.49.33-PM-1280x540.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-4.49.33-PM-768x324.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-4.49.33-PM-1536x648.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-10-at-4.49.33-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在影片中可見，用家可以在仿似冒險樂園的掟彩虹枱上無限掟幣，並可以移動視角從不同的角度觀看代幣是否能夠「中獎」或有否「砸界」，亦包括日前掟彩虹爭議中的俯視角度。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_49674"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h4qMuKXhVV4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>在該段 1 分鐘的短片中，操控者不斷掟出多個代幣，而代幣會在桌上殘留一段時間並消失。在期間僅有數個位於最大紅色區域的代幣能夠符合「中獎」要求，而沒有其他區域的代幣中獎。</p><p>在民 BK Hong 的影片簡介可見，模擬器是由 UE 5.3 製作，並參考了去年一名屋宇裝備工程師<a href="https://elvissharing.blogspot.com/2022/02/misc-bs.html?m=1">計算掟彩虹機率的文章</a>。而該文章計算的結果如下，約以每個代幣 $1 計算，掟中綠色區域的期望值為 $965，以大獎藍色區域的機率更是 $20775。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://youtu.be/h4qMuKXhVV4?si=yZSlkGmTKjAmplVq">YouTube</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
